Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,beloved doctor and susan thank you for letting us say goodbye to you by expressing a gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,from our hearts i want to begin with the tribute to you from someone who couldn't be here today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but who loves you very much michael beckwith michael beckwith is the founder of the agape
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,international spiritual center here is his tribute to you it is my joy david to speak directly to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,on this extraordinary occasion of your last public appearance while you may think that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,disappearing from the public eye the energy frequency of your love compassion and wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,remains in every heart you have touched throughout these
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,many years and certainly that includes my own and that of my spiritual community
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you are a cosmic blessing on the planet a beneficial presence whose imprint is deep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and eternal i love you brother i love you god bless god bless michael beckwith god bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,brother and now we have a ceremonial tribute from south korea they're going to do a special
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what honey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,oh boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that's terrific
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much i'm greatly honored that's beautiful thank you i'm greatly honored
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,god bless you ladies thank you very much are they from korea thank you ladies then the buddha called
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and andah and said to him it may be ananda that after my passing away you might think gone is the utterance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of our master we have no master anymore but you should not think so ananda for the doctrine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and discipline which i've taught you and prescribed to you will be your master after my death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,now amongst i exhort to you exhort you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,all compounded things are subject to decay work for your salvation with honestness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,these were the buddha's last words but for the presence of saints on earth the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,would burn to death we pray for you so long as we live we live in your remembrance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:05:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and on our death be blessed with your vision god bless his three hearts god bless this react
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you i don't want to lose this stuff water from the ganges river as everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:06:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,knows the ganges river is blessed and calibrates extremely high what is the
