Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ganges river calibrates at 700 because of the sacredness of its dedication thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on behalf of all the followers of dr david hawkins teachings from india
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,dr hawkins teachings have touched the beginners in the spirituality starting from the beginners
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the spirituality up to the scholars who spend years in studying the scriptures in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they become very exponents when we have distributed the books of dr hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to the beginners they felt that it has cleared many of their spiritual doubts and it has inspired
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,them touched them and transformed them equally so when these books have been given to the scholars
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who had spent years in the research in spirituality they also felt that it has touched and transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,them and whatever they have learned all these years in their spiritual research they could find
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the same teachings in dr david hawkins books and they felt touched and transformed what we have
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,done is we have integrated dr hawkins teachings along with the indian scriptures and then we have
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,spread this message to many youngsters and adults and old people alike and all of them have been
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,uplifted and greatly benefited by dr hawkins teachings which makes the scriptural understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,much more simple much more easier and more clear so on behalf of all the followers i offer humble
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,prostrations and respects to dr david hawkins for making a great difference in all of our lives and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,may your teachings be with us forever because we have already integrated them into our regular
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,satsangs and spiritual discourses and workshops and so on and so forth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and seminars and so on and so forth so we continue to feel your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and we continue to feel your blessings hario god bless you god bless you god bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,god bless you god bless you god bless you god bless you god bless you god bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the water from the ganges as everyone here knows calibrates extremely high calibrates at 700
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that's incredible incredible here's march brit it is such a great honor to be here with you today
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,dr david hawkins i'm dr marge britt i'm the minister senior minister of unity in tuxton california where
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you came to speak at our center in 2003 you have been one of the most profound spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in christians day in the church you have been one of the most profound spiritual teachers in christians day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of my entire life, and your teachings from the moment that I found them have impacted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the teachings that I do in Unity and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:10:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As the vice president of our international seminary, I'm also aware of the impact that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you've had worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my fondest memories of you is when you came to Unity Village to meet with students
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and with the hierarchy of Unity School of Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We were between meetings, going from meeting with the students to a meeting with the hierarchy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,walking quickly to get to the next meeting, and suddenly you disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone looked around to try to find you, and we located you a few moments later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In the rose garden, smelling the roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have always brought beauty and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your energy, your consciousness, your vibration was a match for Unity, and is a match for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,New Thought, and is a match for Christianity, and I cannot thank you enough for what you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You have given, in the world, how you have made the teachings of Jesus and other master
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers literally come alive through your very being and your very consciousness, and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be eternally grateful for you and for Susan, who said to you, you must write, and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you must teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see you, I just don't remember who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see you now, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a few students from South Africa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more students back at home, and your work is spreading slowly but surely, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just want to thank you from the bottom of my heart for everything that you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything you've given us and all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the Channel Islands in the United Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Channel Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Channel Islands in the United Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Channel Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of the United Kingdom, would all the students from the United Kingdom like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they say, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to say thank you and your work will live on in our hearts and it is a pleasure to live your truth. Amen. God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello Dr. Hawkins, hello Susan. We are coming from Germany and also on behalf of all the German Dr. Hawkins students and the rest of the European students, we'd like to say thank you very much for all you have done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have changed our life and we are grateful beyond words. Maybe all the European students would like to stand up now and thank our teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Guten Abend. Danke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in the medical field and I've had the opportunity to see how much these ideas can help patients who are working on different issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's so many ways, but of them all, I think the main help they've given...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What they've got is to be introduced to the idea that the ego comes from the animal level, as so many are locked in guilt, self-hatred and judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's explained to them that the ego comes from the animal, that it's a very good animal, it's very good at what it does, there's no need to hate it or to destroy it, but to understand it and just disengage from it has been most helpful, probably of all that I've done with them over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And also they can make friends with their little animal, and I tell them that Dr. Hawkins loves talking to his little teddy bear, and he'll say to it, they cut you off in traffic, of course they should be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it softens it for them so much. Sometimes they go on and buy books and DVDs to study further, and then I know they're going to learn in a hundred different ways that all healing is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:16:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For one reason only, the love of God. So on their behalf, and mine too, Dr. Hawkins, thank you so much for your life's work and for all you've given us. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins. Hello, everyone. I was asked to speak briefly on what I witness as a psychotherapist, so I thought I'd ask all psychotherapists to please stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if all psychotherapy patients...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If all psychotherapy patients can please stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's so many things to say, but as a therapist, Dr. Hawkins, you give such reverence and respect for the full spectrum of physical, mental, spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:17:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can say as a therapist, so many patients have benefited from simply seeing a psychiatrist and getting on medication, and many more have benefited from availing themselves of 12-steps work and spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing I'd just like to add is that Dr. Hawkins often says, of course, it's not where you are as a clinician, it's where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've found your work profound in helping me to meet clients where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And really the simple things, using humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've basically pretended like every joke you've ever said is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I crack your jokes in sessions all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you also say, Dr. Hawkins...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That deep down what we all want is a recognition of what we truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like as a therapist, I'm a witness to the truth of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that love really does heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And that we just really need to step back and allow love to do what love does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, we're here representing all the families who are raising children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And doing the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And one teaching that's been very beneficial to me is knowing that all that I have to do is be the very best wife that I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And be the very best mother that I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is uplifting mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And so parenting with Dr. Hawkins' work has meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It has meant for us that the kids never ask us to go on any vacation, but instead to go to the Buddha relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It has also meant that they always remind us to forgive everybody whenever they get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And more than anything, it has taught us to practice unconditional lovingness and to see divinity in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just on the isolated mountaintop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins said one time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is no greater gift to give to mankind than to perfect this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the greatest gift we have received is to be allowed to witness that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste, Dr. Hawkins, Susan, and everyone at Veritas Pub.
