Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,thank God for dr. Hawkins and so say all of us thank you dr. Hawkins thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,dr. Hawkins thank you dr. Hawkins thank you thank you thank you god bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,durable adorable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Luke Nakahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am from Dallas, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And two and a half years ago, I was a broken, lost, and confused man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And Karen O'Brien, a good friend of mine, was kind enough to introduce me to the teachings of you, Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and to introduce me to Susan and the wonderful people at Veritas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to keep it brief, but I have dedicated my life to serving God,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to serving my fellow man, to serving myself, and to taking care of all the lovely creatures on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you so much, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been with no medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:23:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to suffer from depression, clinical depression, all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I read Power vs. Force, and I think there's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to take any medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suffer panic attacks anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I jump, and I enjoy life, and I'm set free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know that depression is a disease that we cannot see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's inside us, that hole that eats us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to thank you for my freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for my health and to show me the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Canadian, and we have a bunch of Canadians here, Mexicans and Canadians.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Race, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:23:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins and Susan, I come to thank you not by myself, for my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.61,0:24:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the members of our church that are here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.57,0:24:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And, Lord, I come to thank you for my teaching from the consciousness of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.90,0:24:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way I know how to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.96,0:24:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is to express it from my heart, because words, language cannot do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Lord, I give you my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.98,0:24:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.55,0:24:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the mic a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.84,0:25:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I testify that you are the Lord, and I love you more than my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.26,0:25:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.35,0:25:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just want to say, Dr. Hawkins, what a beautiful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.78,0:25:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful life that you've shared with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I speak for most, many people, all the friends that I know that follow your
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.07,0:25:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.07,0:25:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to separate where you begin and end in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.45,0:25:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's every single part of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.49,0:25:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Every choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.45,0:25:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.21,0:25:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this life has been transformed due to being a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.65,0:25:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is absolutely amazing, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.73,0:26:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.70,0:26:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing Grace, how sweet the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.70,0:26:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How sweet the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.70,0:26:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How sweet the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.70,0:26:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How sweet the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.70,0:26:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How sweet the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.70,0:26:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How sweet the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.90,0:26:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That deed that's saved a wretch like me is blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.70,0:26:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I'm saved, who can say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.60,0:26:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From a caver after a storm close to my house made in Minnesota, St. Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.42,0:26:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.80,0:26:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Dr. Hawkins and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.60,0:27:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, ah, maybe the last time that I see you physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.40,0:27:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I meet you daily inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.57,0:27:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.06,0:27:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And my life has been changed in beautiful ways since I came to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.63,0:27:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.98,0:27:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.05,0:27:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, my name is Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.38,0:27:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say that the book Power vs. Force changed my life for the better,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.89,0:27:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as I suspect it did for many of the people sitting in this audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.10,0:27:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to just express how profoundly grateful I am for it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.89,0:27:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and for your decision to teach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.82,0:27:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also want to thank Susan for the large body of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.69,0:27:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which will take me the rest of my life to study and comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.73,0:28:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So just thank you, and what a blessing you are to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.32,0:28:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.25,0:28:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation from what felt like a weak, lost, messed-up inner child has been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.09,0:28:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your presence in my life has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.94,0:28:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.28,0:28:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me, among other things, how to focus, how to be strong, how not to crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.01,0:28:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me to be present, to walk through fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.75,0:28:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to walk right through the inner and debilitating emotional storms that once were overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.69,0:29:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have gifted me perseverance, but not the way that was previously thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.23,0:29:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.06,0:29:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As a dramatized endeavor, but you taught perseverance as in devotion and steadfastness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.94,0:29:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to the greatest love of all, and to facing life, and to learning to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.25,0:29:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me how to love myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.92,0:29:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, you taught me how to walk straight ahead, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.14,0:29:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowing God to take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.57,0:29:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.08,0:30:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my teacher forever, for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.32,0:30:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.34,0:30:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a treasured and beautiful lighthouse, and I am forever grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.92,0:30:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo, until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.52,0:30:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my name is Brian Atkins from Austin, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.91,0:30:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is some of the group from Austin, and there's several of us in Austin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.65,0:30:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lubbock, where I'm originally from, and Dallas, and just all over Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.36,0:30:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.70,0:30:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to share the first time I came to Sedona to see Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.57,0:30:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd seen you once before, but you came around and shook everyone's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.00,0:31:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And as soon as you shook my hand, this incredible, loving energy just flooded through my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.46,0:31:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just felt like it started expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.75,0:31:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, I've been coming here as much as I possibly can for the past six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.29,0:31:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And each time I've had a huge shift like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.79,0:31:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've helped me through a lot of really rough troubles I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.27,0:31:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've helped me to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.46,0:31:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of all, you've helped me to not take myself so seriously and have humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.91,0:31:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just wanted to express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.04,0:31:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm really going to miss being able to come here to see my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.73,0:32:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really feel now that you've also helped me find the teacher within.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.07,0:32:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the most valuable gift I could ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.98,0:32:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm eternally grateful as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.68,0:32:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.16,0:32:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.74,0:32:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first discovered your teachings, I was a person very devoted to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.58,0:32:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was following.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.71,0:32:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.15,0:32:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading political works like Noam Chomsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.13,0:32:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Following that as truth, I was a very confused person.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.80,0:32:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I had had some spiritual experiences that I did not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.27,0:32:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And just had a lot of emotional problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.90,0:32:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And over the course of the past six years, seven years, it's just been transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.05,0:32:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, you've really given me, you know, like Ben said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.25,0:33:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.14,0:33:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't separate your teachings from my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.96,0:33:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've seen the impact they've had through me on my family, on my friends, on my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.11,0:33:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.74,0:33:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've given us the gift, me the gift of freedom to trust myself and to love myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.31,0:33:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And to live a life of service, helping others to experience joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.34,0:33:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.32,0:33:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.69,0:33:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.24,0:33:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.50,0:33:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.52,0:33:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.54,0:33:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.56,0:33:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.58,0:33:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.60,0:33:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.67,0:33:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.75,0:33:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.97,0:33:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.00,0:33:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.02,0:33:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.47,0:33:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I look forward to continuing being in the flock here in this life and hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.43,0:33:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.22,0:33:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.57,0:34:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of Amsterdam, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.24,0:34:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of Iran, thank you very much for bringing clarity and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.15,0:34:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And making spirituality fun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.90,0:34:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.69,0:34:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello again, dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.88,0:34:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And my name in this lifetime is Stephanie, in an Atlantis that was Alta Hamir, and would
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.90,0:34:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,just like to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.90,0:34:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you for all you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.55,0:34:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I promise that I will continue to transmit your love frequencies everywhere that I travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.63,0:34:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.63,0:34:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.63,0:34:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she from?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.23,0:34:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.23,0:34:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.55,0:34:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.55,0:34:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,South Korea, I think he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.05,0:34:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.05,0:34:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.05,0:34:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've given me everything I've ever wanted for a whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.05,0:34:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.05,0:35:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.57,0:35:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.11,0:35:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.67,0:35:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.67,0:35:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm from Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.67,0:35:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My testimony is two years ago, my best friend and I came to Conference on Peace, we kind
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.94,0:35:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of bet a large, like a gamble on life because I believed in the truth that I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.55,0:35:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So once we came here and had the effect, we went back home and we're very successful in
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.15,0:35:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.15,0:35:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've both become very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.26,0:35:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.30,0:35:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've got to share that love for the율 cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.38,0:35:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.38,0:35:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,physical training with others
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.01,0:35:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.73,0:35:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,coherences come from that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.05,0:35:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.32,0:35:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much just like he said
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.13,0:35:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we kind of like
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.19,0:35:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,going on this path together like we're best
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.21,0:36:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,friends but
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.15,0:36:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to say thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.26,0:36:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.28,0:36:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and Susan thank you for your
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.36,0:36:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,divine energy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.28,0:36:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for bringing sanity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.36,0:36:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,into our family
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.42,0:36:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes only one person
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.51,0:36:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and through your divine guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.17,0:36:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.42,0:36:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have brought
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.63,0:36:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,peace and joy into our
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.55,0:36:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,family and my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.09,0:36:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,loves you now
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.46,0:36:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also thank you for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.67,0:36:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.53,0:36:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and joy as a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.30,0:36:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to this creation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.32,0:36:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and to all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.00,0:36:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.46,0:37:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as a gratitude to your
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.59,0:37:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,work I would like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.84,0:37:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone to join
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.05,0:37:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hawkins and Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.40,0:37:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,into a few moments
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.40,0:37:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of stillness and peacefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.32,0:37:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.50,0:37:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste Dr. Hawkins, Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.34,0:37:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,my name is Judy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.17,0:37:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,this is my husband Charlie
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.67,0:37:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,words could never express
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.30,0:37:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,my love and gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.48,0:37:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for your work and for your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.53,0:37:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.34,0:37:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and there were two words that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.42,0:37:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you wrote in Power vs. Force
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.19,0:37:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that changed my entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.61,0:37:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and those two words were
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.92,0:37:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without exception
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.32,0:38:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was how to walk on the path
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.92,0:38:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.55,0:38:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,first you said you could only talk
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.61,0:38:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,from personal experience
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.30,0:38:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the practice
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.19,0:38:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the first was a desire
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.40,0:38:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,became intense
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.67,0:38:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the practice of unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.09,0:38:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.55,0:38:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,without exception
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.05,0:38:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.28,0:38:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,even my daughters and my children
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.15,0:38:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you drive me crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.36,0:38:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I kept hearing you say
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.15,0:38:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without exception
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.32,0:38:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that practice is a lifelong practice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.82,0:38:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a psychotherapist
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you've changed my entire practice
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.57,0:38:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,my entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.11,0:38:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and just as a regular person
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.63,0:38:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on behalf of all of humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.75,0:38:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much for your gift
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.63,0:38:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,love you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.44,0:38:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.42,0:38:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,my father was an Episcopal priest
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.94,0:38:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I was raised in the Episcopal Church
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.57,0:38:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and sang in choirs just like you did
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.76,0:39:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but it wasn't until
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.96,0:39:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I came into your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.30,0:39:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that I began to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.94,0:39:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,take myself less seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.21,0:39:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.67,0:39:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for your incredible lightness of being
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.82,0:39:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,for your sense of humor
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.48,0:39:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for being the fool
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.67,0:39:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in the divine court of our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.01,0:39:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.15,0:39:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.46,0:39:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.48,0:39:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,he who dwells in the protection of the Most High
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.57,0:39:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,shall abide under the shadow of the Almighty
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.61,0:39:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.50,0:39:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.48,0:39:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.71,0:39:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,your work facilitated a profound spiritual experience
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.94,0:39:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.50,0:39:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and from that I was able to stop drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.26,0:39:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and get into a program
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.26,0:40:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and today I'm not the most loving person
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.13,0:40:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm going that way
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.36,0:40:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a God in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.34,0:40:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.82,0:40:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as God goes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.05,0:40:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to see and feel him in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.30,0:40:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's a result of everything you've given to me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.19,0:40:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm eternally grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.53,0:40:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.07,0:40:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.84,0:40:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.13,0:40:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at age 18
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.26,0:40:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was kicked out of my house
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.65,0:40:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have five siblings
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.07,0:40:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and mom and dad's still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.78,0:40:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent several decades
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.11,0:40:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to overcome resentments and anger
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.38,0:41:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and with some progress
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.48,0:41:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,until you know the next thing would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.65,0:41:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd get kicked in the gut
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.94,0:41:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I found your work
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.26,0:41:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the map and your lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.23,0:41:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it became very obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.11,0:41:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that everyone's just doing the best that they can
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.26,0:41:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the transformation in my family
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.71,0:41:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has just been phenomenal
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.11,0:41:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the best relationship with my mom and dad
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.92,0:41:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've ever had
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.46,0:41:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in weekly communication or more
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.21,0:41:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and with my siblings
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.15,0:41:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's all gone just incredibly well
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.80,0:41:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know I speak for many here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.76,0:41:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're a father figure to me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.96,0:41:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and have taught me a lot about strength
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.09,0:41:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and courage and tenderness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.61,0:41:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.80,0:41:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.84,0:42:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there are no words worthy of expression
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.80,0:42:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of what I found within through your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.03,0:42:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc and Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.53,0:42:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.03,0:42:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years of my life in addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.55,0:42:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,over 5 years of that time
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.88,0:42:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,shooting heroin
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.55,0:42:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in and out of jails, living on the street
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.80,0:42:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,by the mercy of the Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.92,0:42:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was exposed to your teachings in rehab
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.96,0:42:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a few years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.96,0:42:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I now live a sober life
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.98,0:42:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,full of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.07,0:42:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you brought me to Christ, you brought me to Krishna
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.50,0:42:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you brought me to the rooms of recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.09,0:42:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and the steps of recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.30,0:42:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wake up in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.80,0:42:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,grateful to be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.07,0:42:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was condemned to the life I was living
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.82,0:42:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for the rest of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.01,0:42:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wake up a free man
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.63,0:42:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,by your grace
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.13,0:43:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you saved my life
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.34,0:43:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.48,0:43:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,firstly they got me out of atheism
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.15,0:43:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,using logic
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.96,0:43:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and reason
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.46,0:43:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and also for about
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.05,0:43:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,25 years
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.17,0:43:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of panic and fear
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.07,0:43:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which manifests itself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.09,0:43:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in irritable bowel syndrome
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.63,0:43:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and using your
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.36,0:43:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,techniques that you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.44,0:43:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,described in
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.76,0:43:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,handling major life crises
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.59,0:43:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in about 5 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.09,0:43:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to handle that fear and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.86,0:43:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and just like you state
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.90,0:43:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,just look straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.05,0:44:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to God and just ignore the energies
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.88,0:44:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and they
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.23,0:44:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.34,0:44:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they dissipated
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.44,0:44:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and in about 5 years
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.57,0:44:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to transcend something
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.07,0:44:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that had really ruled my life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.75,0:44:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for 25 years
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.21,0:44:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so thank you so much for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.42,0:44:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.90,0:44:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,dear Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.42,0:44:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and dear Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.28,0:44:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.30,0:44:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,from the depth
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.61,0:44:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.40,0:44:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.15,0:44:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for what I have given
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.65,0:44:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and what I have gained from you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.09,0:44:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.48,0:44:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,my life has changed so much
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.19,0:44:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's indescribable
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.78,0:44:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.34,0:44:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I love you both
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.38,0:45:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I love all of you too
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.69,0:45:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an alcoholic
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.21,0:45:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and a heroin addict
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.96,0:45:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and a crackhead
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.98,0:45:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and my name is Danielle
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.98,0:45:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I heard one of your recordings
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.23,0:45:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,8 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.36,0:45:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and your consciousness communicated with mine
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.48,0:45:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I received the gift of inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.13,0:45:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't stop drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.92,0:45:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't stop using
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.92,0:45:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but I also couldn't stop listening
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.48,0:45:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't stop reading
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.96,0:45:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I came and I saw you for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.32,0:45:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,years later
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.32,0:45:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I left
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.32,0:45:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I left with the gift
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.32,0:45:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of desperation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.51,0:45:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think how I used to think
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.51,0:45:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel how I used to feel
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.51,0:45:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't act how I used to act
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.51,0:45:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know that you gave me those two gifts
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.69,0:45:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and God did the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.69,0:45:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and today I love
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.05,0:45:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I give
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.05,0:45:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I tell people about the teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.30,0:46:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.65,0:46:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.65,0:46:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.65,0:46:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,when I first came to your lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.65,0:46:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in 2005
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.65,0:46:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.65,0:46:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was seeking a teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.59,0:46:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.59,0:46:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and you told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.59,0:46:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,what I seek I will find
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.59,0:46:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm grateful to God's grace
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.59,0:46:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that he's brought Dr. Hawkins to me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.61,0:46:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as a spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.61,0:46:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could have continued
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.61,0:46:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,this journey
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.61,0:46:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,this spiritual journey
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.61,0:46:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,without Dr. Hawkins as a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.61,0:46:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and his inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.61,0:46:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and his guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.13,0:46:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,his divine guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.13,0:46:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the incredible energy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.63,0:46:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.63,0:46:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the divine presence
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.63,0:46:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that emanates
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.63,0:46:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it always puts me into
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.63,0:47:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.17,0:47:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,my life's been changed
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.17,0:47:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,through his teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.17,0:47:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been following a spiritual path
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.17,0:47:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,most of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.17,0:47:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was very fortunate
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.17,0:47:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to have good teachers along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.17,0:47:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel that Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.17,0:47:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is my last and final teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.17,0:47:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will follow his teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.17,0:47:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,forever
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.15,0:47:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.32,0:47:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.32,0:47:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.28,0:47:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,greetings Dr. Hawkins from New Zealand
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.51,0:47:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a poet
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.51,0:47:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but the last few days
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.51,0:47:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a few lines have been running around in my head
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.51,0:47:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so I put them on paper
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.51,0:47:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowing that this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.51,0:47:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,was going to come
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.86,0:47:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,reflections on the impact
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.86,0:47:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of the writings of Dr. David R. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.86,0:47:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the clarion call rises
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.51,0:47:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the challenge made in every book
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.51,0:47:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,straight and narrow is the path
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.51,0:47:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,waste no time
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.51,0:48:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but dear friends
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.63,0:48:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the path has been so brightly lit
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.63,0:48:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by the divine words
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.63,0:48:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,within these works of devotional non-duality
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.63,0:48:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for this life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.17,0:48:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the straight and narrow path
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.17,0:48:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,rises effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.17,0:48:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to meet every step forward
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.17,0:48:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.46,0:48:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,every stalled step
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.46,0:48:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and to guide the gathering pace
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.63,0:48:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of growing consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.63,0:48:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,outwardly
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.88,0:48:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a newly found
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.98,0:48:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,constant smile
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.98,0:48:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,echoes the flow of growing love
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.98,0:48:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,inwardly
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.34,0:48:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,peace and joy endure despite
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.40,0:48:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the artful challenges of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.40,0:48:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding shifts to knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.50,0:48:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and being
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.50,0:48:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how pure
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.17,0:48:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how true the experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.17,0:48:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of devotional non-duality
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.17,0:48:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.17,0:49:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,my husband and I give thanks for you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.63,0:49:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,every night in our prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.63,0:49:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel compelled to express my gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.63,0:49:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,towards you in person
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.21,0:49:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it is challenging to find words
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.69,0:49:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to express how eternally grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.69,0:49:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am for the both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.98,0:49:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and for the work
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.98,0:49:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I must be blessed with excellent karma
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.13,0:49:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to have found your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.13,0:49:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so young in life
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.13,0:49:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you have shown me how
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.82,0:49:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to recontextualize my entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.82,0:49:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that has made all the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.82,0:49:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it hasn't been an easy trip
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.82,0:49:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel that you have provided me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.82,0:49:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with the proper tools
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.82,0:49:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to survive on the sometimes treacherous
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.82,0:49:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but mostly beautiful journey
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.82,0:49:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the tools you have given me include
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.07,0:49:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a shield that cannot be punctured by doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.26,0:49:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a helmet full of knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.46,0:49:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to know who and what to avoid
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.46,0:49:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a compass whose only direction is truth
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.61,0:49:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,shoes made of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.61,0:50:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that only follow the straight and narrow path
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.65,0:50:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the greatest tool of all
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.65,0:50:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.65,0:50:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a love that I can't even begin
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.65,0:50:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to express in two words
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.05,0:50:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you with every ounce of my existence
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.05,0:50:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I love you both so very much
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.05,0:50:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,please wait for everybody in the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.05,0:50:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to get a full gear for ours
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.05,0:50:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you're welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.40,0:50:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.23,0:50:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say hello or goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.23,0:50:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.23,0:50:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to just say goodbye to the crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.23,0:50:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.11,0:50:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks to the Lord God
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.11,0:50:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for the loving presence
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.63,0:51:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks to thee oh Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.07,0:51:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for thy loving presence
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.42,0:51:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for that is what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.40,0:51:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the loving presence
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.40,0:51:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of God Almighty
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.82,0:51:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for which I am eternally grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.82,0:51:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you in the name of the Father
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.82,0:51:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the Son
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.82,0:51:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.82,0:51:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.82,0:51:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.94,0:51:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the pipes stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.36,0:51:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,can you hear the pipes?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.36,0:51:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they better
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.36,0:51:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'll kill them
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.86,0:51:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you know God bless the pipes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.26,0:52:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they calibrate at 500?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.92,0:52:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.92,0:52:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.69,0:52:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they calibrated 500 right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.69,1:00:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so go out to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.05,1:01:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and spread the word
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.94,1:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,change people's lives like we have done
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.42,1:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you've heard the testimony
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.42,1:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the results
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.42,1:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's up to each one of you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.13,1:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to change someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.13,1:01:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,now that yours has been changed
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.13,1:01:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the last 10 years that we have done this
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.34,1:01:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,has been so rewarding to us
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.34,1:01:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I could just pass that along
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.34,1:01:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how rewarding this whole change will be
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.34,1:01:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to do the same
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.34,1:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all it takes is just one person
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.07,1:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to help one person to change one life
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.61,1:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to change one life around
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.67,1:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we love you all
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.05,1:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we wish we could continue but we can't
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.88,1:02:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be in our hearts forever
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.46,1:02:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and we will see your faces in our dreams
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.46,1:02:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we carry all your spirits with us
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.15,1:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and hope we meet again
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.19,1:02:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,love to you all
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.19,1:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,do I get up?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.42,1:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.92,1:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,by your love
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.71,1:03:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm greatly honored by your love
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.15,1:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you now
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.65,1:03:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and forever
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.65,1:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of my Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.19,1:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.73,1:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.32,1:04:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.25,1:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen
